data.title: President's and Dean's List Announcements
data.text:
Students eligible for President's or Dean's List designations are invited to create an announcement for sharing via social media or other outlets.

The announcement lists are posted one week after final grades are due in the spring and fall semesters. These lists include matriculating undergraduate students enrolled in 12 or more academic credits who do not have open grades (I, IP, or RD). Students who have requested that their educational records be designated as “Confidential” are not included in these public lists.

Please note that transcripts include President's and Dean's List designations as well and can be ordered here.
